My wife and I, we just...

07:46.268 --> 07:48.034
<i>Folks, we're now making
our final descent</i>

07:48.036 --> 07:49.603
<i>- into Indianapolis.
- We're taking a trip to Rome.</i>

07:49.605 --> 07:51.338
