07:51.340 --> 07:53.039
People back home will see you the way...

08:11.421 --> 08:12.854
Hello?

08:18.462 --> 08:19.594
Mom?

08:38.448 --> 08:39.448
Dad!

08:46.356 --> 08:48.456
